    "description": "PharmEasy Ventures Solutions, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Backend Developer for our Bhubaneswar operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout PharmEasy Ventures Solutions:\nPharmEasy Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with PharmEasy Ventures Solutions!",
